16
00:00:47,429 --> 00:00:50,390
The story of how all these kids went from being out of the school

17
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:52,530
to successfully completing Year 12,

18
00:00:52,990 --> 00:00:54,689
and many then on to further education,

19
00:00:55,229 --> 00:00:55,990
captivated me.

20
00:00:57,789 --> 00:00:59,850
As a father of four school-aged children,

21
00:01:00,229 --> 00:01:01,869
the idea that our kids would have a voice

22
00:01:01,869 --> 00:01:02,909
in their own learning environment

23
00:01:02,909 --> 00:01:04,750
and that their teachers would collaborate,

24
00:01:05,170 --> 00:01:07,030
share ideas and work together

25
00:01:07,030 --> 00:01:07,590
on the best outcomes,

26
00:01:07,609 --> 00:01:08,549
for everyone,

27
00:01:08,989 --> 00:01:10,590
was a lightbulb moment for me.

28
00:01:11,269 --> 00:01:11,609
A leader,

29
