31
00:01:15,390 --> 00:01:16,250
meaning to guide,

32
00:01:16,549 --> 00:01:16,829
educate,

33
00:01:17,250 --> 00:01:17,530
teach,

34
00:01:17,769 --> 00:01:18,689
and draw out information,

35
00:01:19,090 --> 00:01:20,030
was born out of this.

36
00:01:20,769 --> 00:01:21,170
Together,

37
00:01:21,469 --> 00:01:23,129
Matt and I have had the great privilege of working

38
00:01:23,129 --> 00:01:25,250
with thousands of leaders in education,

39
00:01:25,629 --> 00:01:25,989
sport,

40
00:01:26,310 --> 00:01:26,709
industry,

41
00:01:26,909 --> 00:01:27,430
and the arts.

