00:01:52,489 --> 00:01:54,209
at the South Adelaide Football Club.

51
00:01:54,250 --> 00:01:54,989
Is that your recollection?

52
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:56,290
I think so, mate.

53
00:01:56,329 --> 00:01:59,969
I remember meeting you at a game against Sacred Heart

54
