00:02:33,990 --> 00:02:36,229
But you stood up for me at a young age,

71
00:02:36,530 --> 00:02:38,189
and I never forgot that,

72
00:02:38,250 --> 00:02:39,490
because you were in my corner,

73
00:02:39,689 --> 00:02:42,009
and it never lost me that you were the person

74
00:02:42,009 --> 00:02:43,789
that came and extended that hand of friendship

75
00:02:43,789 --> 00:02:45,270
when others weren't prepared to do it.

76
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:46,849
I do remember it, mate.

77
00:02:46,969 --> 00:02:48,849
And yeah, I remember it fondly.

78
00:02:48,849 --> 00:02:49,610
And so,

79
00:02:49,629 --> 00:02:50,530
I'm really glad I did, really.

80
00:02:50,729 --> 00:02:51,849
I mean, I just,

